t;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea298ad50adf0134d7a41c2" style="width: 298px; height: 193px;"/></strong></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">先修课和实习也不能落下，建议大家先了解不同项目的要求，至少修一门编程语言、数据库语言以及数据结构课。因为大一大二大部分精力都在学习上，我实习开始的也比较晚。当时导师给了我很多资源，在申请的过程中也是需要花费精力的，包括改简历、推荐信、去学习面试的思路技巧。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">这个过程也让我成长了许多，更感谢老师全程保驾护航啦，在面试后也辅导我去和面试官跟进结果、写感谢信等。现在看来，这里面门道不少，建议大家多问多了解，尽力做到周全。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">最后不得不说的就是语言考试了。因为我本身是英语专业，所以对我来说算是小 case，两个月就解决了 GRE 和雅思。说实话，我的单词量不算大，不太喜欢刻意背单词，复习 Verbal 的时候基本是靠自己的语感，分析词根、发音等方去判断词性。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">备考雅思时我着重练习的就是写作，主要按照一位外国雅思考官出的全英教材去练习，每个句式、例题一个个都过了一遍，最后考了 7 分。所以我建议底子不错的同学，都尽量去搜集外国考官出的教材。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea298e550adf0134d7a41c6" style="width: 352px; height: 239px;"/></strong></span></strong><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我相信很多同学不仅仅是把英语当做申请的一项工具，更想精益求精，将它作为自己的兴趣，毕竟英语不只是用在申请时，它会一直跟随你的未来。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我觉得英语水平最本质的差别就在于英语的阅读量，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我一直很喜欢读英语小说，已经养成了阅读习惯。悄悄说一句，其实我是英剧同人文的 cp 粉~（有点羞涩），所以没事儿就会在同人文网站上泡着，久而久之就积累了语感，英语已经成了一种语言载体，这时你看到英语就会很亲近。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以英语的学习是一种习惯和长期坚持的过程，一定要尽早培养使用它的习惯，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">这样你对它的认识就不会只局限在背单词、刷题、应付考试的层面上，而是真正有了英语思维~ 这样不仅申请起来更加得心应手，未来的学习和工作都会受益无穷。</span></p><