                          <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section></section><section>    <section>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大二寒假时，我曾去香港短期交换一周。作为在本地读书的上海人，那是我第一次真正意义上离开家，过上独立生活，那种自由快活的感觉把我迷住了。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">那也是我第一次见到没有明确界限的大学校园，从那时起，我就渴望能出国读研。</span></span>    </section>    <section>        <br/>    </section>    <section>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">很多学生，尤其是双非院校的学生，会反感“双非逆袭”这一标签，但我完全不会。尽管我也高考发挥失常，但我觉得，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一件事情既然发生了，那么你所能做的就只有接受它，弥补它。</span></strong></span>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">国内院校用 985 / 211 / 双非来区分学校；在申请时，国外一些院校对于双非同学要求更高，我觉得这是正常的。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不这样做，对那些高考成绩优秀的同学来说，不也是一种不公平吗？</strong></span>    </section>    <section>        <br/>    </section>    <section>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px;">不管在哪里，你都要尽力保持优秀。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在大二寒假之前，我并没有出国读书的念头，但当时我的 GPA 就已经很高，也已经有了很多实习、竞赛的经历。</span>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <p>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这些积累让我在申请路上走得更为顺畅，也让我从中收获了很多东西。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">接受自己的劣势，然后弥补它，这才是“双非逆袭”的真正内涵。</strong></span></span>    </p>    <p>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></span>    </p>    <p>        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span s