, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:18px"></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>                            </p>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">目前为止，我只参加过一次面试，来自哥大。然而就是这唯一一次面试，我还惨烈<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“翻车”</strong>了。</span>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">面试当天，我超级紧张。因为申请季的跨度很大，从语言考试到申请再到面试，中间漫长的时间导致我已经很久没有开口讲英语。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">但当天</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">真正让我崩溃的是，面试时我的网卡了……</strong></span>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">尽管模拟面试时，Vince 老师有培训我在网络不好时应该怎样判断情况、怎样和对方解释，但那讲的是网络略有不佳的情况，而我的情况要严重得多。</span>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; marg