n: center; white-space: normal;"></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>                            </p>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">不过幸好有<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">模拟面试培训</strong>，让我不至于彻底心态崩溃，顺利完成了语音面试。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">模拟面试使我收获良多，Vince 老师帮我指出了英语发音问题，教给我回答问题的一些技巧，比如一个问题怎样在两分钟内回答结束，如何描述一件事情会更吸引人等等。</span>                            </section>                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <br/>                            </p>                            <p></p>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在 Vince 老师的指导下，我还<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">分类准备了题库</strong></span>，面试时有一半问题我都准备过，这成了我最终致胜的法宝。</span>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我命由天不由我？</strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong>                            </p>                            <section>                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">申请季真的充满意外。不到最终尘埃落定的一刻，什么都有可能发生。</span></strong>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">刚准备留学时，香港也在我的考虑范围之内，并且我选了很多香港学校作为目标院校。但由于某些众所周知的因素，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我不得不放弃香港学校</span>，增补了一些英国和澳洲的院校。</span>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">除了一些不可控因素外，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">语言考试的屡战屡败也完全在我意料之外。</strong></span>我是一个比较有计划性的人，在准备申请时自己心里就有规划蓝图，但我确实没有想到，语言考试会拖累我整个申请季。</span>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我首考雅思就拿到 7 分，但之后不管我怎么复习，怎么努力，成绩都毫无寸进，令我非常挫败；而更令我崩溃的是，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">GMAT 我考了五次，竟然是第一次分数最高。</strong></span></span>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <br/>                            </p>                            <p></p>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这些经历告诉我，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">人不要对自己的能力过度自信，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“语言成绩会越刷越高”很可能只是你的一厢情愿</strong>，现实往往是在压力之下会越考越崩溃，越到后来越难调整。</span></span>                            </section>                            <section>                                <br/>                            </section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">回顾我的申请之路，我觉得的确是“我命由天不由我”，任何事情都会发生，个人计划也要考虑时代进程。</span>                            </section>                            <p></p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea139587bab207e954ba6c6" style="width: 723px; height: 429px;"/></strong><br/>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;">（图源网络，侵删）</span></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></strong>                            </p>                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-h