="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以后来就决定出国留学。</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea036fdefe95515770986c9" style="width: 504px; height: 421px;"/></span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></strong></span></p><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;"><br/></span></section><p></p><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__33" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在考虑申请专业的时候接触到了视觉传达，了解之后发现，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">视觉传达设计远不是我们以前理解的那样，仅仅停留在二维纸媒上。随着新媒体的发展，视传的范围变得越来越广泛，内容也越来越丰富有趣了。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__34" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__35" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于我来说，视觉传达会通过各种媒介给人造成视觉上的冲击力，能够达到吸引人眼球、引人入胜的效果。比起科技类的展示，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我个人更偏向文艺类的视觉表达作品，</span><span class="js_darkmode__36" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以后来我就决定把视传作为自己的研究生专业。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__37" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__38" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我平时很喜欢去看展，看展对于我来说是娱乐也是学习的过程。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__39" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__40" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">2018 年的时候，我在香港理工大学的设计专业毕业展上看到有一个毕业生</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">以女性身体为灵感，设计出了一系列日常用品，</span><span class="js_darkmode__41" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如凳子、脚垫等等。我觉得设计师的理念是想让大家用客观、充满美感的眼光去看待女性的身体，希望把一些从前大家谈之色变的东西变得日常化。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">设计师用作品表达自己思想的行为，是他们和世界交流的一种方式，而这样的交流方式让我觉得很受触动。</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea0376befe95515770986ce" style="width: 557px; height: 561px;"/></span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></p><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__43" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><br/></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__44" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">另外，随着现在沉浸式体验的流行，也为我做设计带来了很多灵感。我在 2019 年去上海看了一个名字叫做</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“感官边界”</span><span class="js_darkmode__45" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">的展，这个展厅的正中间放着一个透明的圆球，圆球上面有一个个圆形的铅笔头，参观者通过转动圆球在空间里留下痕迹。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">受这种沉浸式体验的启发，我把与交互相关的设计运用到了自己的毕业设计中。</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea037b0efe95515770986d3" style="width: 609px; height: 610px;"/></span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></p><p></p><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这些经历在某种程度上开阔了我的眼界，也让我意识到自己的不足，希望通过努力学习来提升自己。</span><span class="js_darkmode__47" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">国外的艺术氛围比国内浓重得多，国内的设计行业感觉还是比较商业化的，而我更偏向艺术表达的风格，这就坚定了我出国学习的想法。</span></section><section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="text-align: center;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center;">                        <strong>被棕榈的“靠谱”感动</strong><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center;">                        <strong><br/></strong>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section></section><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__49" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在大二上学期有了出国的想法之后就开始咨询作品集中介，综合别人的经验和自己的实际情况列了一个时间表，打算先考语言然后再去做其他事情。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__50" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__51" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">虽然计划做得很好，但我是一个拖延症很严重的人，第一次裸考雅思考了 6 分之后就把留学的事情暂时搁置了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一直到大二暑假的时候才开始准备作品集，用了将近两年的时间才真正完成作品集。</span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__52" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">也因为拖延症的关系，我直到大三下学期在作品集老师的催促下，才想起来要赶紧找留学中介准备申请的事情。</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></strong></span><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea0380defe95515770986db" style="width: 629px; height: 742px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></p><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__54" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__55" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">认识棕榈是经人介绍的，我最初</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">对棕榈印象最深的就是棕榈的导师制。</span><span class="js_darkmode__56" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">咨询的老师告诉我申请的过程中会有 4~5 个导师来跟进我的学习，其中包括了主导师和专业导师。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我觉得这样的模式分工明确，给人感觉很靠谱。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></section><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__57" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我身边也有在 DIY 留学的同学，他们得靠自己去收集资料、独自完成整个申请的流程，就像之前说的那样，我是一个有拖延症的人，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我需要有人在申请的过程来引导我，帮助我完成整个流程。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__58" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__59" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">棕榈让我感觉很好的一点就是，导师在签约之前很详细地和我解释了许多细节，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">让我了解到自己能够参与到整个申请过程，而不是把所有东西都甩给棕榈。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__60" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__61" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这种个人定制的模式就消除了我的一些疑虑，比如担心自己的材料被胡乱处理之类的。而且棕榈没有那种强制推销的感觉，这样还让我觉得还蛮舒服的，于是就这样决定和棕榈签约了。</span></section><p>    <br/></p><p>    <br/></p><p></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong style="white-space: normal;">在 Viva la&nbsp;Vida 的日子</strong></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong style="white-space: normal;"><br/></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong style="white-space: normal;"><br/></strong></p><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__64" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大三的时候，棕榈帮我内推了一个叫</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“ Viva la vida ”&nbsp;</span><span class="js_darkmode__65" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">的线上志愿者活动。这是一个和艺术相关的公益活动，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">活动内容是在全球收集生命画像，即每个人按照自己对生命的理解以画画的形式表达出来。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__66" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__67" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我很感谢棕榈给我提供了这一次实习的机会，因为艺术类的实习非常难找，而且大多数都在北上广深之类的城市。我直到大三才意识到要去丰富实践经历，但当时我的语言和作品集都没做完，时间很紧迫，所以只能参加线上实习。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__68" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__69" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">工作过程中让我印象最深刻的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">是泰国一个小学里小朋友们画的生命画像。</span><span class="js_darkmode__70" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于小朋友来说，他们对生命的理解可能就是长大后会成为什么样的人，收集上来的画像里有足球运动员、医生、护士、老师等等，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">你能透过这些画感受到小朋友的纯真和善良，让人觉得特别感动。</span></section><p></p><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea0385befe95515770986df" style="width: 465px; height: 616px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">（来源：VIVA 画出生命 公众号）</span><br/></p><p></p><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__72" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在整理作品的过程中，我发现虽然大家对生命的理解都不一样，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但很多人会用到“爱心”这个元素。</span><span class="js_darkmode__73" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这和视觉设计有点像，即设计师有时会用同一个元素去表达自己的观点，从而引起大家的共鸣，多样化的表达中又存在着共性，这样很能打动人心。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__74" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__75" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这就是这个实习带给我的收获，让我在一个有趣、多元的环境中愉快地完成了工作，同时又觉得非常有意义。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__76" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong>写文书是挖掘亮点的过程</strong></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong><br/></strong></p><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__78" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">棕榈在文书这块帮了我很大的忙，因为我的个人经历其实还是蛮单薄的，参加的比赛没有得到很好的奖项，实习经历也不是很多，如果光靠自己来写文书可能两三百字就写完了。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__79" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">好在我的主导师在帮助我梳理个人经历的时候，会和我一起挖掘亮点，引导我该怎么写。</span><span class="js_darkmode__80" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">听了主导师的分析之后我发现，其实自己的经历并没有那么贫瘠，还是可以从中挖掘出闪光点的。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__81" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__82" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如我在文书里提到的“涂鸦大赛”是主导师帮我梳理的。在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“涂鸦大赛”</span><span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">里，我需要做的是联系和组织不同专业的同学、协调组内分工，同时自己也要参与设计，比赛后期还要负责报道和宣传。</span></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><p style="text-align: center;">    <span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea038a0efe95515770986e5"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span class="js_darkmode__83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></span></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__85" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一开始我觉得“涂鸦大赛”并不是什么含金量很高的比赛，整个过程也没什么亮点，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但是主导师通过对比赛过程中的细节进行梳理，帮助我拉通逻辑线条之后，我发现其实这个经历锻炼了我的领导能力、展现了自己的才华。</span><span class="js_darkmode__86" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">就这样，本来算不上非常出彩的“涂鸦大赛”经历变得更加具体、生动了。</span></section><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__87" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span class="js_darkmode__88" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经过导师的点拨后，我的文书就能够写得很顺了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为导师已经帮助我整理好了框架，只要再在这个框架里填色就好了。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="js_darkmode__89" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">所以我个人感觉在写文书这块，导师起到非常大的作用，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为光靠自己一个人想的话在思维上难免会有局限性，</span><span class="js_darkmode__90" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一些实习经历按照自己的语言写出来可能就是 X 年 X 月在 X 地担任了 XXX 职位，这样看起来就非常的空洞、不具体。导师在这个方面上帮助我细化了很多内容，让我写的东西看起来更真实、更丰满。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="js_darkmode__90" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#feffff;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="">选校的关键是要找准定位<br/><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#feffff;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style=""></strong></span></span></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__93" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我学校最终确定的时间比较晚，一直到去年的 12 月份才最终确定下来。我当时是参考了主导师提供的选校表，再根据以前对一些院校的了解，物色了几个觉得还不错的学校。</span></section><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__94" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">值得一提的一点是在一开始选校的时候，我对自己的实力处于什么样的水平并没有一个清晰的把握。</span><span class="js_darkmode__95" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来我的专业导师看了我的作品集，再结合我个人的实际情况和我客观分析了一下，让我对自己有了一个算是比较准确的认识。</span></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#feffff;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style=""><br/></strong></span></span><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea0398aefe95515770986ed" style="width: 527px; height: 659px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">(学员供图，未经允许不得转载)</span></p><p></p><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__97" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来，导师给我提供了一个选校规划表，里面的学校都是他们根据我的情况为我挑选的学校，其中包含了冲刺档、稳健档以及保守档，我就可以根据这个再结合自身情况来进行选择。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></section><section>    <br/></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在我收到的 offer 里，萨凡纳给我提供了奖学金，</span><span class="js_darkmode__98" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我很喜欢他们的校园环境，校园里的硬件设施条件也很不错。但萨凡纳并不是一个纯做艺术的学校，他们的商业氛围比较浓，算是一半艺术一半商业的样子。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">如果后面没有收到 Pratt 的 offer 的话，我也许会选择去萨凡纳。</span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></section><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea039ddefe95515770986ef" style="width: 704px; height: 469px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;">（来源：SCAD 官网）</span></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Pratt 相对于萨凡纳来说，他的艺术氛围要浓厚得多，</span><span class="js_darkmode__99" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">而且 Pratt 在纽约，看展会很方便。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">另外，Pratt 很注重不同学科之间的相互交流，</span><span class="js_darkmode__100" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为不同领域之间的碰撞往往能激起许多意想不到的火花，这一点很对我的胃口。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 147, 147); font-size: 12px;"><span class="js_darkmode__100" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong>疫情也拦不住希望降临</strong><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong><br/></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong></strong></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__104" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">今年申请季赶上了新冠肺炎，而我刚好又在武汉，所以在等待 offer 的这段时间里还蛮丧的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">连最坏的打算都做好了，但一想到几年的努力很有可能就这样白费了，心里又很不甘心。</span></section><p></p><section>    <span class="js_darkmode__105" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></section><section>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我常常会去问主导师和文书老师各种问题，他们每次都很耐心和辅导和回答我的问题，</span><span class="js_darkmode__106" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">包括现在